{"tid":2372992,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公屋走廊雜物充斥惡臭擾鄰 恐成爆疫溫床","createTime":"2021-01-20T06:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T10:52:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7dcbe170e35f59440f5b12e67bcd27e0db56a8e2","tid":2372992,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T06:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TYAqau.Dbt5vCuaA9jb7_A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-01/b96505e0-5ab8-11eb-ae7d-b59122db17b1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FTYAqau.Dbt5vCuaA9jb7_A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-01%2Fb96505e0-5ab8-11eb-ae7d-b59122db17b1&h=d4c7a448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肺炎疫情嚴峻之際，有市民疑漠視環境衞生，把雜物檢回家中存放，結果因單位雜物充斥，戶主「被迫」在樓層公眾走廊煮食，從而令樓層環境烏煙瘴氣，一旦細菌孳生，恐隨時引發播毒危機。<br />\n<br />\n居於石硤尾大坑東邨東健樓的陳先生表示，一名疑有拾荒習慣的鄰居，經常把紙皮、舊電器等雜物檢拾回家，日積月累下，已放滿單位及堆疊在窗戶之外，有人惟有把雜物擺放在公眾走廊及電梯大堂。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，單位戶主由於在屋內寸步難行，故日常煮食均在走廊進行，更甚者晚上更把尼龍床被鋪等移放走廊，把公眾地方變成私人臥室。堆放在單位及走廊的雜物不時傳來陣陣臭味，亦有不少蟑螂自單位內竄出，在目前疫情爆發的高危情況下，衞生情況令人堪憂。<br />\n<br />\n屋邨物業服務辦事處早前在公眾地方張貼告示，要求物主在24小時內搬走雜物，否則會列作廢物清理而不作另行通知。根據「屋邨管理扣分制」，住戶在公眾地方棄置雜物及垃圾會被扣5分。<br />\n<br />\n《東網》正就事件向屋邨物業服務辦事處、房屋署及涉事戶主了解。"},{"pid":"bacb048daa0f6d2a4dfec92c90c622f2d074e9d9","tid":2372992,"uid":41368,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T06:46:20.000Z","msg":"公屋根本就係一班cls廢老嘅集中地"},{"pid":"4ba5439ae91f5e5d0c361845eae203b36d14b9bc","tid":2372992,"uid":269202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T06:48:12.000Z","msg":"如果係非租置公屋，係咪無管理公司同法團？"},{"pid":"514d8ce7529ee36ca6b8bc3c20153f8c0a5c918e","tid":2372992,"uid":14739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bacb048daa0f6d2a4dfec92c90c622f2d074e9d9","tid":2372992,"uid":41368,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T06:46:20.000Z","msg":"公屋根本就係一班cls廢老嘅集中地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T10:49:41.000Z","msg":"都有d 正常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b278032d1b3079b876efb92952b31bb97ff6a7","tid":2372992,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"514d8ce7529ee36ca6b8bc3c20153f8c0a5c918e","tid":2372992,"uid":14739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bacb048daa0f6d2a4dfec92c90c622f2d074e9d9","tid":2372992,"uid":41368,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T06:46:20.000Z","msg":"公屋根本就係一班cls廢老嘅集中地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T10:49:41.000Z","msg":"都有d 正常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T10:50:24.000Z","msg":"好快會俾佢哋逼到痴線"},{"pid":"60a5f134d561b0eee352802106b64d86a147635e","tid":2372992,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"勁鐘意大坑東邨啲間隔 好好住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}